<B>AUTHOR'S CREDENTIALS</B><P>

James Nicholson has been an industry analyst for the last seven years.  Mr. Nicholson is the 
Editor of NDT Update, a monthly newsletter covering industrial testing and measurement, 
published by Quantum Publications, New York, NY.  He also provides market consulting 
services for companies in the lasers, electro-optics, and inspection and measurement fields.  
This is his third report for BCC.<P>



